{"tid":152044,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人懷疑自己有抑鬱症？","createTime":"2017-03-11T11:52:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T23:58:00.000Z","uid":63271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d524d5d5ecd2259e11c25c2a082e388747df5d91","tid":152044,"uid":63271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T11:52:23.000Z","msg":"睇過下d症狀都中中地，但又未算好嚴重<br />\n不過心情長期都低落<br />\n成日想變，但係好頹廢，唔想放棄自己呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔敢同人講，連網上都唔想講<br />\n會唔會只係個人太孤獨而唔係抑鬱？（未去到所有事都提唔起勁去做）"},{"pid":"657bf24f696c1b4309e15e224fffba0eedbccc13","tid":152044,"uid":84568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T11:59:25.000Z","msg":"我試過同人講 我懷疑自己有病<br />\n人地會話 真正有病嘅人係唔會覺得自己有病<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48ed86a2ef220c247923ebb1736f6dcc0aa0f07","tid":152044,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:01:38.000Z","msg":"懷疑就去同醫生講<br />\n同朋友什至網上既人講 你想對方比咩回應你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b7eaf54549a25111f2a3cb4eab76254bd4c2b4","tid":152044,"uid":35816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:07:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>懷疑就去同醫生講<br />\n同朋友什至網上既人講 你想對方比咩回應你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇下有冇相關人士分享經驗姐<br />\n自已食緊西藥(半年)  唔想睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f865c20a747590354b218ed122d46db0cdf581","tid":152044,"uid":35816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:08:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>懷疑就去同醫生講<br />\n同朋友什至網上既人講 你想對方比咩回應你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇下有冇相關人士分享經驗姐<br />\n自已食緊西藥(半年)  唔想睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同樓主差唔多情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都係驚要食藥"},{"pid":"ddedccc7b2a6820018eca380e6fee8054bfb33f7","tid":152044,"uid":63271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:11:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>懷疑就去同醫生講<br />\n同朋友什至網上既人講 你想對方比咩回應你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有d野好難開口，對我黎講，好難打開心扉"},{"pid":"801d73b4919d679b1220dbc560c06ea7d95ad2ed","tid":152044,"uid":16085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:12:54.000Z","msg":"搵多啲朋友兄弟家人陪住 情況舒服既不妨講下心事，日常軼事又好，讀書工作亦好<br />\n<br />\n睇下有無咩活動，例如音樂運動旅行行山個啲持續咁可以一大班人咁做/練<br />\n<br />\n搵多啲野做/學等自己累，失眠個啲都會有改善<br />\n<br />\n當然，睇下家庭醫生都唔會錯"},{"pid":"96eba5f4a78a26bb0e010bea78fa7246eb3e8d28","tid":152044,"uid":63271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:13:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我試過同人講 我懷疑自己有病<br />\n人地會話 真正有病嘅人係唔會覺得自己有病<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之後點？你既健康情況<br />\n不過呢句都幾on9，佢講緊精神病呀？"},{"pid":"2dba9ea22709682b1d8681c3ea12556e06ebe0d7","tid":152044,"uid":52448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:26:18.000Z","msg":"會唔會就係屈住冇發洩D唔開心出黎所以令個人感覺好抑鬱啊?"},{"pid":"87120667fb6bdda1beb9381bc4ad41e4696ebf01","tid":152044,"uid":15800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:36:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一自己一個就會好down<br />\n有時自己係屋企好驚自己暈左冇人知<br />\n成日啦覺得自己好冇用，又會係度喊<br />\n<br />\n有時明明自己冇乜特別事唔開心，又會諗下細個啲唔開心既事，會感覺好down<br />\n同埋好容易比小事搞到自己好annoyed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7bfb8261d16798d1a72e277d62b49e91517fcd5","tid":152044,"uid":41521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:37:18.000Z","msg":"我比我女朋友話我好似有抑鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125b187fa44848d54c5bd76438dae9c7c6591d89","tid":152044,"uid":84021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:44:52.000Z","msg":"唔好亂google左啲病徵就當自己有呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，只會強化呢種負面諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得唔妥，真係搵專業人士幫幫手<br />\n自己黎都得架，身處環境好重要，盡快離開啲負能量，主動「格硬」搵正面野，你會慢慢受正能量影響<br />\n做下運動先！發泄啲垃圾情緒！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抑鬱最可怕係覺得世界絕望，但事實絕對唔係咁既，希望一直係度，你接受佢就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e66bc4f9fa25656e8a406a35170d6fa47926c9","tid":152044,"uid":63271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:53:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好亂google左啲病徵就當自己有呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，只會強化呢種負面諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得唔妥，真係搵專業人士幫幫手<br />\n自己黎都得架，身處環境好重要，盡快離開啲負能量，主動「格硬」搵正面野，你會慢慢受正能量影響<br />\n做下運動先！發泄啲垃圾情緒！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抑鬱最可怕係覺得世界絕望，但事實絕對唔係咁既，希望一直係度，你接受佢就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當然我睇完覺得中中地，不過唔係好相信自已有"},{"pid":"6bc8b11f00a23a519302af383022690f7a96267d","tid":152044,"uid":74172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:57:58.000Z","msg":"你係咪差唔多日日都情緒低落，持續左幾耐"},{"pid":"39e4e80143924971539936d10253a0cab0c9576e","tid":152044,"uid":63271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T13:02:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪差唔多日日都情緒低落，持續左幾耐</blockquote><br />\n無計過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知自已sad左幾耐"},{"pid":"f5ce20fba6227a5d0f27e3c24294e84c4bbd2261","tid":152044,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T13:03:50.000Z","msg":"神經病真的很爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src